lead_paragraph: Mike Napoli hit his first home run of the spring but the Cleveland Indians remained winless after six games following a 6-5 loss to the Milwaukee Brewers on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Mike Napoli Homers but Winless Indians Lose 6-5 to Brewers
